CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper October 15, 1955, pg. 32, reads: "Top Workmanship - A used car comes to an NIADA dealer like Al D'Alessandro, 2115 West Liberty Avenue, and before it is placed in the show room, highly skilled craftsmen put it into A-1 condition. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Man in suit, and mechanics working on two Cadillac cars in Al D'Alessandro car dealership, 2115 West Liberty Avenue, South Hills
